

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    
  This is a C++ program to display image stills captured from the 
  at the speed of 27 microseconds onto a created window screen  named Video
  Apart from this when the 'up arrow' Button is clicked on the keyboard 
  the image is saved in the same directory with name photo.jpg 

   Compile the Program 
      g++ -o my_cheese my_cheese.c -I/usr/include/opencv  -lcv -lhighgui -lcvaux -lml -lcxcore  
   
   Run the executable using 
      ./my_cheese
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
